<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(烹饪用的) 材料；成分：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>fresh / basic ingredients
新鲜食材/基本配料</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(完成某事的) 要素；因素：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Hard work is a vital ingredient for success.
勤奋是成功的一个重要因素。</p></div></div>